Package model

Class SpaceObject

java.lang.Object
model.SpaceObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Satellite
Direct Known Subclasses:
Debris, Payload, RocketBody, Unknown
public abstract class SpaceObject extends Object implements Satellite
The SpaceObject class is an abstract representation of a space object. It implements the Satellite interface and provides common properties and methods for all space objects, such as record ID, satellite name, country, orbit type, and other attributes.
